NOTE ON THE PACKAGED RELEASE (.exe):

The pre-built Windows executable distributed via GitHub Releases bundles
third-party tools that keep their own licenses:

  • yt-dlp   — Unlicense (public domain).            https://github.com/yt-dlp/yt-dlp
  • FFmpeg   — GPL/LGPL (this build: GPL).           https://ffmpeg.org

Because the packaged .exe includes a GPL build of FFmpeg, that binary
distribution as a whole is covered by the GPL. FFmpeg's source is available
at https://ffmpeg.org. The original SWΛYZ Downloader source code in this
repository is provided under the MIT license above.
